title: Success or Death
itunes:title: Success or Death
description:
Episode 396 - This is how our mindsets should be regarding anything important in our lives, either we get it or we fail miserably. Never, and I mean never, should we not get something that we want because of fear or giving up, but because we gave it our all and it didn't work out.
